vienna brain 648 hemp and yankee doodle it urged a complete 
check of chinas computers and disks and asked people to 
immediately report any evidence of tampering with computer programs 
china a nation of 11 billion has only about 300000 
computers only a few state organizations such as the police the 
military and the state statistical bureau have online systems 
connecting computers 
