and disaster checklists were handed out pictures of the october 
earthquake destruction also were on review 
at watsonvilles mobile home park jimmie henson said even 
though wednesdays quakes were smaller than octobers they were 
more destructive for her the tremors caused cracks in the walls of 
her home and broke dishes and other small objects 
im more upset today than i was from the big one much 
more she said 
