when the lawsuit began sophie and milos 
malesevs daughter was in high school when it ended their 
daughters youngest son was in high school and milos had been dead 
for 17 years 
i thought they were waiting for me to die said mrs 
malesev who waited nearly 25 years to settle claims over damage 
