murphy who reports directly to company chieftains michael eisner 
and frank wells and says they realize the amazing responsibility 
we have 
our ability to influence is remarkable and the perception 
people have of us is really hard to live up to murphy said 
has disney done so not entirely he acknowledged 
i think if you ask people does disney recycle they would 
say gee they must if anybody does 
