taxes but then angered locals even more by announcing construction 
of seven more hotels 29 new attractions a fourth amusement park 
and 19000 more workers 
they can go out there and pave over anything they want to do 
without going through any kind of environmental review said bill 
donegan an orange county fla commissioner whoss led an effort 
to make disney more accountable 
we dont know the real impact environmentally we dont know 
how many woodpeckers nests have been destroyed how many eagles 
how many ospreys 
